OL,3,CWill extra powers help London shed the
OL,4,Ctitle of Britain's fly-tipping capital?
OL,6,FThe leader of Brent Council Muhammed
OL,7,FButt said it was hard to go down any
OL,8,Fstreet without seeing littering or fly-
OL,9,Ftipping, adding: "Most councils do
OL,10,Fhave opportunities to take it to a
OL,11,Fwaste tip or call one of our services
OL,12,F- there is no need to fly-tip anywhere
OL,13,Fin the UK."
